title: Lunchbox Talks To People Waiting For Popeye’s Chicken Sandwich + The Vegetable Draft Turns Controversial + Bobby’s Mailbag: Guy Asks Girl Out For Drinks After Car Accident
itunes:title: Lunchbox Talks To People Waiting For Popeye’s Chicken Sandwich + The Vegetable Draft Turns Controversial + Bobby’s Mailbag: Guy Asks Girl Out For Drinks After Car Accident
description:
Lunchbox went out to Popeye’s on the launch of the chicken sandwiches and talked to people who were lined up waiting for it. Our Vegetable Draft turns into the most controversial ever. Bobby opens up the mailbag from a female listener who got into a car wreck and was then asked out for drinks.
